      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, those are perfect examples. I noticed you mentioned how it adapts to \"evolving societal values.\" Some people argue that this is actually a problem because it lets judges basically make up new rights instead of just following the text of the Constitution. How would you suggest I explain that critique to my students so they get a full picture?",
